com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqscscripts

Class MQSCScriptsPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractUIPlugin
      • com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqscscripts.MQSCScriptsPlugin

  • public class MQSCScriptsPlugin
extends AbstractUIPlugin

    The main plugin class for an Eclipse Plugin.

    This initializes the necessary resources for the function of the MQSC Script Projects folder element of the MQExplorer navigation tree. It also provides methods for other classes in this plugin to access those resources.
